        "timestamp": "2017-10-31 13:22:58.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nIs there a separate rule that then captures these rogue abatements and retracts them from memory?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "f150c677cc0555ecec97612fde43077a92c6d807",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 1677,
