          "username": "dc443y"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2017-10-31 13:40:31.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Is there a separate rule that then captures these rogue abatements\n > and retracts them from memory?\n\nGood catch, should we just retract it or does policy need to send a notification?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "782c4071679e17f8a3429b780f833bd646df1eae",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 57,
