          "username": "pdragosh"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-10-31 13:46:24.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWe definitely retract them. We could publish a Reject message so folks know what we did with it. Ideally (future), there would be a policy that dictated what to do but I think for now we just publish a reject. The requirement really should be on DCAE not to do this behavior.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
